text:
2505 Palisade Avenue, south side, east of Independence Avenue. This old frame house was owned by G. E. Mann in 1879, and by D. B. Cox in 1900.

Federal Art Project
"Changing New York"
Berenice Abbott, photographer

title: Bronx: Palisade Avenue.
